title: Ebro In The Morning - Six Fingers + Klutch Sports Agent Nicole Lynn
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/16. 

The crew talks to Klutch Sports Agent & author Nicole Lynn about the NCAA, Young Money, and her new book (21), Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (11:00 & 1:10) and we find out who played themselves (40).

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
